OL,3,CHeads of the Valleys officially opens
OL,4,Cafter more than 20 years of work
OL,6,FThe Heads of the Valleys road has
OL,7,Fofficially opened more than 20 years
OL,8,Fafter work commenced.
OL,10,FWork started on the A465, which runs
OL,11,Fbetween Hereford and Swansea, in 2005
OL,12,Fand has cost around #2bn.
OL,14,FThe latest phase, between Dowlais Top
OL,15,Fand Hirwaun, was officially opened on
OL,16,FThursday, marking the end of the
OL,17,Fproject.
