OL,3,CHeads of the Valleys officially opens
OL,4,Cafter more than 20 years of work
OL,6,FThe project is aimed at connecting
OL,7,Fcommunities by linking the Valleys,
OL,8,FSouth and West Wales, to the English
OL,9,FMidlands.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the opening, Cabinet
OL,12,FSecretary for Transport and North
OL,13,FWales, Ken Skates, said, "Delivering
OL,14,Fbetter transport and fixing our roads
OL,15,Fis a priority for this government,
OL,16,Fwhich is why I am delighted to be
OL,17,Fmarking the completion of what has
OL,18,Fbeen a hugely ambitious road upgrade
OL,19,Fprogramme.
