OL,3,CHeads of the Valleys officially opens
OL,4,Cafter more than 20 years of work
OL,6,F"It's been a complex project, which
OL,7,Fhas not been without its challenges,
OL,8,Fbut is a fantastic example of how
OL,9,Ftargeted investment in road
OL,10,Finfrastructure can deliver benefits on
OL,11,Fso many levels, from providing local
OL,12,Fjobs to improving accessibility,
OL,13,Fsupporting education and skills, as
OL,14,Fwell as delivering environmental
OL,15,Fbenefits.
