OL,3,CHeads of the Valleys officially opens
OL,4,Cafter more than 20 years of work
OL,6,F"Of course, a project of this
OL,7,Fmagnitude is inevitably going to have
OL,8,Fan impact on local residents, and I
OL,9,Fwould like to thank those that were
OL,10,Faffected for their patience. I am
OL,11,Fconfident that once people realise the
OL,12,Fbenefits of this investment, memories
OL,13,Fof any disruption they have
OL,14,Fexperienced will start to fade."
OL,16,FFinance Secretary, Mark Drakeford,
OL,17,Fadded, "Investing in this major
OL,18,Fcapital project has created real
OL,19,Fbenefits for local people. It has
OL,20,Fresulted in #400m for the local supply
OL,21,Fchain and has created 2,200 new jobs.
