OL,3,CHeads of the Valleys officially opens
OL,4,Cafter more than 20 years of work
OL,6,F"Beyond improving transport, this
OL,7,Fproject has built a legacy in the area
OL,8,Fby training over 200 apprentices and
OL,9,Fproviding STEM activities for local
OL,10,Fschools. This shows how our
OL,11,Finvestments are improving more than
OL,12,Fjust infrastructure; they are
OL,13,Fsupporting our communities."
